{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "d7761453-644b-4f58-b08b-79f89db7dff3",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Ultimate Slayer",
      "effect": "Your opponent cannot activate monster effects in response to this card's activation. Send 1 monster from your Extra Deck to the GY, then target 1 monster your opponent controls with the same card type (Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, Pendulum, or Link); shuffle it into the Deck."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Pourfendeuse Ultime",
      "effect": "Votre adversaire ne peut pas activer d'effets de monstre en r\u00e9ponse \u00e0 l'activation de cette carte. Envoyez 1 monstre depuis votre Extra Deck au Cimeti\u00e8re, puis ciblez 1 monstre contr\u00f4l\u00e9 par votre adversaire du m\u00eame type de carte (Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, Pendule ou Lien) ; m\u00e9langez-le dans le Deck."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Ultimativer Schl\u00e4chter",
      "effect": "Dein Gegner kann keine Monstereffekte als Reaktion auf die Aktivierung dieser Karte aktivieren. Lege 1 Monster von deinem Extra Deck auf den Friedhof, dann w\u00e4hle 1 Monster mit demselben Kartentyp (Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, Pendel oder Link), das dein Gegner kontrolliert; mische es ins Deck."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Assassino Finale",
      "effect": "Il tuo avversario non pu\u00f2 attivare effetti di mostri in risposta all'attivazione di questa carta. Manda 1 mostro dal tuo Extra Deck al Cimitero, poi scegli come bersaglio 1 mostro controllato dal tuo avversario con lo stesso tipo di carta (Fusione, Synchro, Xyz, Pendulum o Link); mischialo nel Deck."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Assassina Definitiva",
      "effect": "Seu oponente n\u00e3o pode ativar efeitos de monstro em resposta \u00e0 ativa\u00e7\u00e3o deste card. Envie 1 monstro do seu Deck Adicional para o Cemit\u00e9rio e, depois, escolha 1 monstro que seu oponente controla com o mesmo tipo de card (Fus\u00e3o, Sincro, Xyz, P\u00eandulo ou Link); embaralhe-o no Deck."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Asesina Definitiva",
      "effect": "Tu adversario no puede activar efectos de monstruos en respuesta a la activaci\u00f3n de esta carta. Manda al Cementerio 1 monstruo en tu Deck Extra, y despu\u00e9s selecciona 1 monstruo que controle tu adversario con el mismo tipo de carta (Fusi\u00f3n, Sincron\u00eda, Xyz, P\u00e9ndulo o Enlace); bar\u00e1jalo al Deck."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u6708\u5973\u795e\u306e\u93c3",
      "effect": "\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u306e\u767a\u52d5\u306b\u5bfe\u3057\u3066\u76f8\u624b\u306f\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3092\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044\u3002\u2460\uff1a\uff25\uff38\u30c7\u30c3\u30ad\u304b\u3089\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u308a\u3001\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3068\u540c\u3058\u7a2e\u985e\uff08\u878d\u5408\u30fb\uff33\u30fb\uff38\u30fb\uff30\u30fb\uff2c\uff09\u306e\u76f8\u624b\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3092\u30c7\u30c3\u30ad\u306b\u623b\u3059\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\uc544\ub974\ud14c\ubbf8\ud2b8 \uc2ac\ub808\uc774",
      "effect": "\uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uc758 \ubc1c\ub3d9\uc5d0 \ub300\ud558\uc5ec \uc0c1\ub300\ub294 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uc758 \ud6a8\uacfc\ub97c \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc5c6\ub2e4. \u2460: \uc5d1\uc2a4\ud2b8\ub77c \ub371\uc5d0\uc11c \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b4\uace0, \uadf8 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uc640 \uac19\uc740 \uc885\ub958(\uc735\ud569 / \uc2f1\ud06c\ub85c / \uc5d1\uc2dc\uc988 / \ud39c\ub4c8\ub7fc / \ub9c1\ud06c)\uc758 \uc0c1\ub300 \ud544\ub4dc\uc758 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ub300\uc0c1\uc73c\ub85c \ud558\uc5ec \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \uadf8 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\ub97c \ub371\uc73c\ub85c \ub418\ub3cc\ub9b0\ub2e4."
    },
    "zh-CN": {
